{
  "stem": "12674.3",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So this was something that belonged to the Jewish community center, so nobody came in there to interfere with it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they-- they-- they didn't have any-- they had a Torah, and they had a-- a-- they had a-- they-- they-- they met.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A few people met there every-- every Shabbat for things.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my brother was bar mitzvahed there and-- and things like that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But it was-- there-- there was nobody left.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And half the people that were left probably didn't want to pray.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So you lived your little life in this apartment that we got.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In this apartment that we got, there were-- there were-- we had-- we had two rooms.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "My aunt-- the one Mira-- the one that-- the two people that wound up being Mira's parents had another very big room.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And my-- my uncle that had to come back from-- the oldest brother had left in [NON-ENGLISH]-- he had to come back to Vienna.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then there was another woman.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Her husband had managed to get out of the country, and she was there with her little boy, Mrs.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH], and she had a five-year-old boy and her mother.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were also from [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They lived in another room.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And a family named Schwartz lived in a kitchen and another bedroom.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it-- it was a gypsy existence.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And-- and all of us had a bathroom on the floor that had been a bathroom for the-- for the-- for the-- for the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that's-- that's how we lived, and that's what was there-- there was and since there was nothing else.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And my-- I remember my father was-- was fantastic.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He managed to build us a little refrigerator.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was the-- about the size of this little table here, a little square box.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
